---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="Recipes — Jinghao Wen">
<section class="page active" id="recipes">
  <div class="sec-eye en">From My Kitchen</div><div class="sec-eye zh" style="display:none">来自我的厨房</div>
  <h1 class="sec-h1 en">Recipes</h1><h1 class="sec-h1 zh" style="display:none">菜谱</h1>
  <div class="sec-rule"></div>
  <p class="tarot-intro en">Cooking is another form of attention — to ingredients, to heat, to time.</p>
  <p class="tarot-intro zh" style="display:none">烹饪是另一种专注的方式——专注于食材、火候与时间。</p>
  <div class="card-grid">

    <div class="card-item" onclick="openModal('recipe-steamedfish')">
      <div class="card-thumb"><img src="/images/photos/foods/蒸鱼.jpg" alt="蒸鱼"></div>
      <div class="card-body">
        <div class="card-meta en">Cantonese · Main</div><div class="card-meta zh" style="display:none">粤式 · 主菜</div>
        <div class="card-title en">Steamed Sea Bass</div><div class="card-title zh" style="display:none">清蒸鲈鱼</div>
        <p class="card-desc en">Eight minutes, soy sauce, ginger, and hot oil. The simplest things done perfectly.</p>
        <p class="card-desc zh" style="display:none">八分钟、酱油、姜丝、滚油。最简单的事情做到极致。</p>
        <div class="card-footer"><div class="card-stats"><span class="card-stat"><strong>20min</strong></span><span class="card-stat"><strong>2</strong> <span class="en">servings</span><span class="zh" style="display:none">人份</span></span></div><span class="card-rating">★★★★★</span></div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="card-item" onclick="openModal('recipe-pilaf')">
      <div class="card-thumb"><img src="/images/photos/foods/抓饭.jpg" alt="抓饭"></div>
      <div class="card-body">
        <div class="card-meta en">Uyghur · Main</div><div class="card-meta zh" style="display:none">维吾尔 · 主菜</div>
        <div class="card-title en">Lamb Hand-Pulled Rice (Plov)</div><div class="card-title zh" style="display:none">羊肉手抓饭</div>
        <p class="card-desc en">Lamb, carrot, onion and rice cooked together in one pot. Central Asian comfort food.</p>
        <p class="card-desc zh" style="display:none">羊肉、胡萝卜、洋葱与米饭同锅焖制。中亚的抚慰之食。</p>
        <div class="card-footer"><div class="card-stats"><span class="card-stat"><strong>1.5h</strong></span><span class="card-stat"><strong>4</strong> <span class="en">servings</span><span class="zh" style="display:none">人份</span></span></div><span class="card-rating">★★★★★</span></div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="card-item" onclick="openModal('recipe-roastduck')">
      <div class="card-thumb"><img src="/images/photos/foods/烤鸭.jpg" alt="烤鸭"></div>
      <div class="card-body">
        <div class="card-meta en">Beijing · Main</div><div class="card-meta zh" style="display:none">京式 · 主菜</div>
        <div class="card-title en">Roast Duck</div><div class="card-title zh" style="display:none">烤鸭</div>
        <p class="card-desc en">Air-dried overnight, honey-glazed, oven-roasted. Crispy skin is the whole point.</p>
        <p class="card-desc zh" style="display:none">隔夜风干、蜂蜜上色、烤箱烘制。脆皮是一切的意义所在。</p>
        <div class="card-footer"><div class="card-stats"><span class="card-stat"><strong>overnight + 2h</strong></span><span class="card-stat"><strong>4</strong> <span class="en">servings</span><span class="zh" style="display:none">人份</span></span></div><span class="card-rating">★★★★★</span></div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="card-item" onclick="openModal('recipe-lambchops')">
      <div class="card-thumb" style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,#3d1a0a22,#6b2a0a11);"><div class="card-thumb-emoji">🍖</div></div>
      <div class="card-body">
        <div class="card-meta en">Xinjiang · Main</div><div class="card-meta zh" style="display:none">新疆 · 主菜</div>
        <div class="card-title en">Grilled Lamb Chops</div><div class="card-title zh" style="display:none">烤羊排</div>
        <p class="card-desc en">Cumin, chili flakes, salt. Nothing more is needed.</p>
        <p class="card-desc zh" style="display:none">孜然、辣椒碎、盐。不需要更多了。</p>
        <div class="card-footer"><div class="card-stats"><span class="card-stat"><strong>30min</strong></span><span class="card-stat"><strong>2</strong> <span class="en">servings</span><span class="zh" style="display:none">人份</span></span></div><span class="card-rating">★★★★★</span></div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="card-item" onclick="openModal('recipe-handlamb')">
      <div class="card-thumb" style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,#5a3a1a22,#8b5a2a11);"><div class="card-thumb-emoji">🥩</div></div>
      <div class="card-body">
        <div class="card-meta en">Mongolian · Main</div><div class="card-meta zh" style="display:none">蒙古 · 主菜</div>
        <div class="card-title en">Hand-Pulled Lamb</div><div class="card-title zh" style="display:none">手抓羊肉</div>
        <p class="card-desc en">Boiled whole, pulled by hand, dipped in garlic and vinegar. Nomadic and primal.</p>
        <p class="card-desc zh" style="display:none">整块水煮，徒手撕扯，蘸蒜醋而食。游牧本味。</p>
        <div class="card-footer"><div class="card-stats"><span class="card-stat"><strong>2h</strong></span><span class="card-stat"><strong>4</strong> <span class="en">servings</span><span class="zh" style="display:none">人份</span></span></div><span class="card-rating">★★★★☆</span></div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="card-item" onclick="openModal('recipe-mouthwater')">
      <div class="card-thumb" style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,#7c3d2822,#8b1a1a11);"><div class="card-thumb-emoji">🍗</div></div>
      <div class="card-body">
        <div class="card-meta en">Sichuan · Cold Dish</div><div class="card-meta zh" style="display:none">川味 · 凉菜</div>
        <div class="card-title en">Mouthwatering Chicken</div><div class="card-title zh" style="display:none">口水鸡</div>
        <p class="card-desc en">Poached chicken, Sichuan chili oil, numbing peppercorns, sesame paste. Cold and alive.</p>
        <p class="card-desc zh" style="display:none">白斩鸡、四川辣椒油、花椒、芝麻酱。凉而鲜活。</p>
        <div class="card-footer"><div class="card-stats"><span class="card-stat"><strong>45min</strong></span><span class="card-stat"><strong>3</strong> <span class="en">servings</span><span class="zh" style="display:none">人份</span></span></div><span class="card-rating">★★★★★</span></div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="card-item" onclick="openModal('recipe-steak')">
      <div class="card-thumb" style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,#3a1a0a22,#5a2a0a11);"><div class="card-thumb-emoji">🥩</div></div>
      <div class="card-body">
        <div class="card-meta en">Western · Main</div><div class="card-meta zh" style="display:none">西式 · 主菜</div>
        <div class="card-title en">Pan-Seared Steak</div><div class="card-title zh" style="display:none">干煎牛排</div>
        <p class="card-desc en">Cast iron, high heat, butter basting. Medium-rare or nothing.</p>
        <p class="card-desc zh" style="display:none">铸铁锅、大火、黄油淋制。五分熟，别无他选。</p>
        <div class="card-footer"><div class="card-stats"><span class="card-stat"><strong>20min</strong></span><span class="card-stat"><strong>1</strong> <span class="en">serving</span><span class="zh" style="display:none">人份</span></span></div><span class="card-rating">★★★★★</span></div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="card-item" onclick="openModal('recipe-hunanbelly')">
      <div class="card-thumb" style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,#8b3a1a22,#6b1a0a11);"><div class="card-thumb-emoji">🍲</div></div>
      <div class="card-body">
        <div class="card-meta en">Hunan · Braised</div><div class="card-meta zh" style="display:none">湘式 · 红烧</div>
        <div class="card-title en">Hunan Red-Braised Pork</div><div class="card-title zh" style="display:none">湘式红烧肉</div>
        <p class="card-desc en">Doubanjiang, dried chilies, and dark soy. Spicier and more aggressive than Shanghainese.</p>
        <p class="card-desc zh" style="display:none">豆瓣酱、干辣椒、老抽。比上海红烧肉更辣、更烈。</p>
        <div class="card-footer"><div class="card-stats"><span class="card-stat"><strong>2.5h</strong></span><span class="card-stat"><strong>4</strong> <span class="en">servings</span><span class="zh" style="display:none">人份</span></span></div><span class="card-rating">★★★★★</span></div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="card-item" onclick="openModal('recipe-dongpo')">
      <div class="card-thumb" style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,#8b1a1a22,#7c1a1a11);"><div class="card-thumb-emoji">🍖</div></div>
      <div class="card-body">
        <div class="card-meta en">Hangzhou · Braised</div><div class="card-meta zh" style="display:none">杭帮 · 红烧</div>
        <div class="card-title en">Dongpo Pork</div><div class="card-title zh" style="display:none">东坡肉</div>
        <p class="card-desc en">Su Dongpo's recipe, unchanged for a thousand years. Three hours, Shaoxing wine, patience.</p>
        <p class="card-desc zh" style="display:none">苏东坡的方子，千年未变。三小时、绍兴酒、耐心。</p>
        <div class="card-footer"><div class="card-stats"><span class="card-stat"><strong>3h</strong></span><span class="card-stat"><strong>4</strong> <span class="en">servings</span><span class="zh" style="display:none">人份</span></span></div><span class="card-rating">★★★★★</span></div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="card-item" onclick="openModal('recipe-brisket')">
      <div class="card-thumb" style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,#3d6b7c22,#1e3a5f11);"><div class="card-thumb-emoji">🫕</div></div>
      <div class="card-body">
        <div class="card-meta en">Cantonese · Braised</div><div class="card-meta zh" style="display:none">粤式 · 焖制</div>
        <div class="card-title en">HK-Style Beef Brisket Pot</div><div class="card-title zh" style="display:none">港式牛腩煲</div>
        <p class="card-desc en">Daikon, beef brisket, spiced broth. Hong Kong winter in a clay pot.</p>
        <p class="card-desc zh" style="display:none">萝卜、牛腩、香料高汤。砂锅里的香港冬天。</p>
        <div class="card-footer"><div class="card-stats"><span class="card-stat"><strong>3h</strong></span><span class="card-stat"><strong>4</strong> <span class="en">servings</span><span class="zh" style="display:none">人份</span></span></div><span class="card-rating">★★★★★</span></div>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>
</BaseLayout>
